{"tid":2040501,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何超儀指三、四房為「阿三」「阿四」，諷刺探病似做騷","createTime":"2020-05-28T15:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T15:19:21.000Z","uid":215823,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"269405ddad42e7662be44a9090674c54a8a625f0","tid":2040501,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"　　賭王何鴻燊四房一直盛傳不和，原來二房的何超儀對三、四房及同父異母的妹妹何超雲、何超蓮與何超盈等不滿，並強調其母藍瓊纓才是賭王的&ldquo;合法妻子&rdquo;，而賭王轉院也是其母的主意。她又直呼&ldquo;三太&rdquo;陳婉珍及&ldquo;四太&rdquo;梁安琪為&ldquo;阿三、阿四&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n　　何超儀表示因父親年紀大，怕住院會受感染，故拒絶太多家人入內探望，但三、四房子女探病時就算吃了閉門羹，也會在病房外走一圈才離開，吸引傳媒拍照，還諷刺她們穿漂亮衣服及帶男友到醫院就像作秀，所以當日她接賭王出院時見大批傳媒守候即急急離開。<br />\n<br />\n超儀句句有骨，到底她與三、四房弟妹感情如何？超儀寸爆的說，並不認識她們，只識「阿四」（指四太）的何超盈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DQiRsa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DQiRsa.jpg&h=e336d2a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2791ab690fa2d1b0ffb1aebe92defbeadb115f18","tid":2040501,"uid":248670,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"只識「阿四」（指四太）的何超盈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n代表佢地有共同興趣"},{"pid":"666ff8e21e519a8435446d7ceb0cfe6e086227d9","tid":2040501,"uid":189235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"其實大房都真係幾撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3d1730cdb49f0358d47a5ba940091295e12efd","tid":2040501,"uid":55868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"好似叫緊工人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4810922b9b2df36bba49f07eeac7c04ff3cfb884","tid":2040501,"uid":71330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"咁三四房又真係做Show <br />\n全部男女都係食下明星仔 做下KOL<br />\n仲塞老豆食自己隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5250643301566f23e17e228d6dabd8046862b28e","tid":2040501,"uid":349872,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"0f3d1730cdb49f0358d47a5ba940091295e12efd","tid":2040501,"uid":55868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"好似叫緊工人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"阿三以前只係看護，當佢工人唔出奇"},{"pid":"c20d675495ae4fddbc47b261cc03edf11b6fea49","tid":2040501,"uid":349872,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"佢無講錯喎，阿三阿四都無正式注冊"},{"pid":"99a239e8fc496b1409fe20c56fe06fdfcb03e56d","tid":2040501,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"被問到超儀指她與超盈到醫院係博見報，超雲句句有骨說：「可能佢唔係咁清楚啲時間，佢去得少，佢好忙，唔會因為佢咁講唔開心。（佢話唔識你？）可能佢語氣有少少問題，其實我哋都真係唔係太熟。」"},{"pid":"345fd2adcacf87a53300ff1c395bfe22866e5ca8","tid":2040501,"uid":246787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4810922b9b2df36bba49f07eeac7c04ff3cfb884","tid":2040501,"uid":71330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"咁三四房又真係做Show <br />\n全部男女都係食下明星仔 做下KOL<br />\n仲塞老豆食自己隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"睇到塞老豆食飯自己隻手 又諗起張相 好想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cb8e7894768e5c55a33ac9347c7e067e83819f","tid":2040501,"uid":307619,"like":